  "description": "<b>据国外媒体报道，惠普前任董事长、风投机构凯鹏华盈(Kleiner Perkins Caufield &#38; Byers)名誉理合伙人雷&#8226;兰恩(Ray Lane)遭到美国国税局(U.S. Internal Revenue Service)起诉，称其存在非法避税行为，涉及金额高达1亿美元。</b>美国国税局5月6日向税务法院(U.S. Tax Court)提交的法律文件显示，去年12月，兰恩以2.51亿美元的财产损失为由进行避税，其中存在不实成分。<img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2cf2ddcc/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F240221.htm&amp;t=%E6%83%A0%E6%99%AE%E5%89%8D%E8%91%A3%E4%BA%8B%E9%95%BF%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E9%81%BF%E7%A8%8E1%E4%BA%BF%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F240221.htm&amp;t=%E6%83%A0%E6%99%AE%E5%89%8D%E8%91%A3%E4%BA%8B%E9%95%BF%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E9%81%BF%E7%A8%8E1%E4%BA%BF%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F240221.htm&amp;t=%E6%83%A0%E6%99%AE%E5%89%8D%E8%91%A3%E4%BA%8B%E9%95%BF%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E9%81%BF%E7%A8%8E1%E4%BA%BF%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F240221.htm&amp;t=%E6%83%A0%E6%99%AE%E5%89%8D%E8%91%A3%E4%BA%8B%E9%95%BF%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E9%81%BF%E7%A8%8E1%E4%BA%BF%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F240221.htm&amp;t=%E6%83%A0%E6%99%AE